# MiVA local development environment
#
# Google OAuth does not require GCP hosting, but it does require a Google Cloud
# OAuth 2.0 Web Client ID. Use the same client ID in the web app and API.
#
# Web app:
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-oauth-web-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com

# API:
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=your-google-oauth-web-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
